How to contribute ? 
-------------------

1. Open Github account
2. Visit our Git repositories through https://github.com/openpiv
3. Fork your preferable repository (Matlab, Python or C++)
4. Fix, commit, push to your repository and create a pull request. 



Support and documentation
-------------------------

We work on the documentation website: http://www.openpiv.net/openpiv-matlab


How to get support? Where to ask questions?

1. Fill the issues on the respective repository (e..g openpiv-matlab https://github.com/OpenPIV/openpiv-matlab/issues)
2. Write an e-mail to openpiv@openpiv.net


